AlephBsnMapper
public class SingleTableMapper
extends DataWarehouseEnrichmentPlugin

Author:
Scot Dalton SingleTableMapper represents a column to column enrichment based on a give element in the Primo document and a mapped column in the DataWarehouse.

enrich

public Document enrich(Document doc,
                       com.exlibris.primo.api.plugins.enrichment.IEnrichmentDocUtils docUtils)
                throws Exception
Adds mappings provided by the NYU Libraries' Aleph DataWarehouse from Aleph BSNs to result of the first column in the plugins' configured SQL query. Mappings are added to the Document based on the plugins' List of SectionTags.
